<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Critical Security Alert</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f5f5f5; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: white; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545, #c82333); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
    .alert-icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .content { padding: 30px; }
    .alert-box { background-color: #f8d7da; border: 1px solid #f5c6cb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .details-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; }
    .details-table th, .details-table td { padding: 12px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6; }
    .details-table th { background-color: #f8f9fa; font-weight: 600; }
    .severity-critical { color: #dc3545; font-weight: bold; }
    .action-required { background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #dc3545; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 10px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="alert-icon">ðŸš¨</div>
      <h1>CRITICAL SECURITY ALERT</h1>
      <p>Immediate attention required</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="alert-box">
        <h2>Security Event Detected</h2>
        <p><strong>Action:</strong> <%= @alert_details[:action] %></p>
        <p><strong>Severity:</strong> <span class="severity-critical"><%= @alert_details[:severity] %></span></p>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= @alert_details[:timestamp] %></p>
      </div>
      
      <h3>Event Details</h3>
      <table class="details-table">
        <tr>
          <th>User</th>
          <td><%= @alert_details[:user] %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Organization</th>
          <td><%= @alert_details[:organization] %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Resource Type</th>
          <td><%= @alert_details[:resource] %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>Category</th>
          <td><%= @alert_details[:category] %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th>IP Address</th>
          <td><%= @alert_details[:ip_address] %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      
      <% if @alert_details[:details].present? %>
        <h4>Additional Information</h4>
        <ul>
          <% @alert_details[:details].each do |key, value| %>
            <li><strong><%= key %>:</strong> <%= value %></li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
      <% end %>
      
      <div class="action-required">
        <h3>âš¡ Immediate Action Required</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Review the security event immediately</li>
          <li>Verify if this was an authorized action</li>
          <li>Check for any related suspicious activity</li>
          <li>Consider implementing additional security measures if needed</li>
          <li>Document your investigation and response</li>
        </ul>
        
        <a href="<%= audit_logs_url(severity: 'critical') %>" class="btn">View Security Dashboard</a>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>Important:</strong> This is an automated security alert. If you believe this alert was triggered in error, please contact your system administrator immediately.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>BrokerSync Security Monitoring System</p>
      <p>This email was sent to <%= @user.email %> at <%= Time.current.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S %Z') %></p>
      <p>Do not reply to this email. For support, contact your system administrator.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>